title: NHM Murshidabad Jobs 2026 - Apply Online for 10 Block Programme Coordinators Posts
description: The National Health Mission Murshidabad (NHM Murshidabad) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 10 Block Programme Coordinator Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their post-graduation and MBA can apply for the NHM Murshidabad Jobs 2026. The interested applicants can apply in online mode. Here we have mentioned the education details, age limit...
